            <p class="comment-content">极其喜欢！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1121176613">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1121176613" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1121176613" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1121176613">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/153141721/">愿随云</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">言简意赅，分类详细，需要看注解才能看懂。处事，交往，治学……涉及很多方面，适合在睡前看几段，慢慢领会，你看似什么都懂，却能在书中发现自己的问题。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

