    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2025256/" class="title-link">如获至宝</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2025256"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1675873/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1675873-33.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1675873/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">素聞（明照）</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-05-15"
      class="main-meta">2009-05-15 10:22:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2025256_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  收到从新华书店的网络上送来的书，只有这本，如获至宝，既便宜，又好，装帧得古香古色，内页设计得朗润清雅大气潇洒，原文和译文同时刊出，方便对国学感兴趣而又国学基础稍微薄弱的人。  内容，是我早已烂熟于心的。04年从弘一法师的文章中知道《格言联璧》，弘一是我最早知悉...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
